They're not near the base.

::Prowl::

Prowl hears Iris' greeting, glancing at her before his he felt Shadow 
move (he's watching him with his wing orbs). THe Maximal spins around 
and looks at the bot.

Shadow's shot misses Prowl's wing by an inch. Prowl swears under his 
breath, realizing that the shot was heading for Iron Raptor as his 
weapons get a lock on Shadow. Two missiles fire from his missile 
launchers, heading at the bot.

-What do you say, love,- he thinks to Iron Raptor. He wanted to let 
her work with him this time, -Should we take him out together?-
